        <mxCell id="KjTfm_Zc6TkFQScnNaN3-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontColor=#000000;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Heading&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ms-List-page&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;div role=&quot;presentation&quot; class=&quot;ms-List-cell&quot; data-list-index=&quot;3&quot; data-automationid=&quot;ListCell&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div data-testid=&quot;validate-measured-transcript-item-height&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;listItem-3&quot; class=&quot;listItemWithSpeaker-244&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;false&quot; dir=&quot;&quot; data-test-props-issearchenabled=&quot;true&quot; data-test-props-searchresultdata=&quot;false&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; flex-direction: row; padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;rightColumn-3&quot; class=&quot;rightColumn-252&quot; style=&quot;position: relative; width: 492.299px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: anywhere;&quot;&gt;&lt;div data-testid=&quot;entryRenderer&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;baseEntry-370&quot; id=&quot;entry-3&quot; role=&quot;group&quot; aria-label=&quot;LUIS PRESAS LAMAZARES 0 minutos 13 segundos&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 20px; display: flex;&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Voy a dar entonces la explicación. El otro día, yo con Mari, a lo mejor un poquito más también a lo técnico porque le interesaba a ella, saber cómo está eso. Contigo ahí, bueno, en esta sesión voy a quedarme un poco más, un poquito más arriba, porque creo que a nivel funcional, pues nos...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;LUIS PRESAS LAMAZARES 0 minutos 33 segundos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Nos puede ayudar más, no mientras tanto. Bueno, entonces esta es la presentación que nos pasaron. Entonces empiezo a explicar un poquito de qué va esto. ¿Qué es esto de lo de eventos y smart notifications y todo esto? Bien, hoy en día para las.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;LUIS PRESAS LAMAZARES 0 minutos 54 segundos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Transacciones o movimientos que se hacen y vamos a decir que pasan por el autorizador. Se están mandando ciertas notificaciones a los clientes. Por ejemplo, oye, acabas de hacer esta transferencia, hiciste este pago de servicio por tal cantidad, etcétera. Ese tipo de Luego vemos cuáles son los tipos de notificaciones, pues son notificaciones de ese estilo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;LUIS PRESAS LAMAZARES 1 minuto 16 segundos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Relacionadas a transacciones que hizo el cliente. Okey, entonces hoy en día tienen aquí este esquema que son como pues cuatro componentes, ¿no? Por un lado tenemos justo la lo que se genera de evento, compra, retiros, validaciones, rechazos, etcétera.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;CHRISTOPHER RICARDO VALENCIA MENDOZA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sub-entry-3&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;entryText-371 textHoverColor-378 clickableItem-270 flexFill-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Stream Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;1 minut