l-328&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;&quot; aria-setsize=&quot;386&quot; aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; role=&quot;listitem&quot; data-is-focusable=&quot;true&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 3px; width: auto; overflow-wrap: anywhere; min-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;ALCANCE DEL REQUERIMIENTO&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;Basado en la conversación, el alcance queda definido así:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Procesar eventos generados por transacciones del cliente (compras, retiros, pagos de servicios, validaciones, rechazos u otros movimientos que pasan por el autorizador).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Publicar dichos eventos en un MQ existente.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Recibir los eventos desde el MQ mediante un componente disparador de eventos.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Enviar los eventos a un componente intermedio a través de Kafka.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• En el componente intermedio, enriquecer la información recibida antes de que sea usada por el sistema final de notificaciones.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Disponer de un nuevo componente llamado tentativamente &quot;Event Integration Adapter&quot; (nombre sujeto a confirmación por el arquitecto y el DT).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Preparar y actualizar la documentación funcional y técnica (Word y PDF) sobre este flujo, sus mapeos y el comportamiento.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Ajustar eventualmente el nombre del microservicio y sus referencias dependiendo de la decisión del arquitecto.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;No se menciona el alcance del canal final al cliente (SMS, push, email), por lo tanto no se incluye.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__hr&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; width: 715px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;HISTORIA DE USUARIO&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;(Construida únicamente con lo descrito en la conversación)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;Como sistema de notificaciones,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;quiero recibir eventos de transacciones enriquecidos y estandarizados,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;para poder generar notificaciones al cliente cuando realice operaciones como compras, retiros, pagos o validaciones.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;Criterios de aceptación identificados:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Debe recibirse un evento proveniente del autorizador a través de MQ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El evento debe ser procesado por el disparador y enviado a Kafka.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El componente de enriquecimiento debe completar los datos necesarios.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El sistema final debe poder usar esos datos para generar la notificación.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El nombre del componente &quot;Event Integration Adapter&quot; debe ser confirmado o actualizado.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Debe existir documentación actualizada (Word + PDF).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__hr&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; width: 715px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;CASOS DE USO&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ol&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Recepción de evento de transacción&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Un evento se genera por una operación del cliente.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Se publica en el MQ existente.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ol&quot; start=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Procesamiento en el disparador de eventos&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Una pieza del sistema toma el mensaje del MQ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Lo envía hacia Kafka para su posterior procesamiento.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ol&quot; start=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Enriquecimiento de la información&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El componente intermedio recibe el evento desde Kafka.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Agrega datos adicionales requeridos para las notificaciones (los detalles exactos no se mencionan).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Entrega el mensaje enriquecido al sistema que enviará la notificación.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ol&quot; start=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Preparación y mantenimiento de documentación&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Se actualiza el archivo Word con la definición del flujo y mapeos.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Se genera el PDF final para entrega.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El equipo de desarrollo puede ajustar mapeos o documentación si surgen cambios tras pruebas.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__hr&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; width: 715px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;ACUERDOS FUNCIONALES&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Los eventos enviados corresponden a transacciones del cliente (compras, retiros, pagos, validaciones, rechazos).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El proceso actual utiliza MQ para la publicación inicial de eventos.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El flujo continúa mediante Kafka para el procesamiento siguiente.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El componente responsable del enriquecimiento agregará datos que hoy no se envían desde el autorizador.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• La documentación será entregada actualizada (Word y PDF).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• El nombre &quot;Event Integration Adapter&quot; es provisional hasta la validación por parte del DT.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__hr&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; width: 715px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;ACUERDOS DE ARQUITECTURA&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Uso de MQ para la publicación de eventos desde el autorizador.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Uso de Kafka como bus de eventos intermedio entre el disparador y el componente de enriquecimiento.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Existencia de un componente nuevo (nombre provisional: Event Integration Adapter).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• La arquitectura aún está en revisión por el arquitecto del proyecto y el DT.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Se buscará influir para mantener el nombre propuesto del microservicio y evitar retrabajo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;• Si el arquitecto asigna otro nombre, deberá ajustarse la documentación y el código.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__hr&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; width: 715px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inhe