        <mxCell id="KjTfm_Zc6TkFQScnNaN3-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontColor=#000000;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ol&quot; start=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Puntos tratados&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Actualmente las transacciones generan eventos que se publican en un MQ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Existe un disparador que toma dichos eventos y los envía hacia Kafka.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• En un segundo componente se realiza el enriquecimiento de la información.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Se está definiendo un nuevo componente con nombre provisional: Event Integration Adapter.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• El nombre final del componente está en revisión por el DT y el arquitecto.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• La documentación (Word y PDF) debe actualizarse; Mari realizará ajustes finales.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Luis buscará al arquitecto para intentar conservar el nombre propuesto y evitar retrabajo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• En pruebas podrían requerirse ajustes mínimos a mapeos o documentación.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-with-markdown&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;ol class=&quot;answer-with-markdown__ol&quot; start=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: decimal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Acuerdos&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Mantener el flujo: MQ → Disparador → Kafka → Componente de enriquecimiento.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Continuar con el nombre Event Integration Adapter mientras se confirma con arquitectura.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Luis gestionará la revisión con el arquitecto para definir el nombre definitivo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;IBM Plex Sans&amp;quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-feature-settings: &amp;quot;liga&amp;quot;; font-size: 1rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); letter-spacing: 0.16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;• Mari actualizará el documento Word y generará el PDF final.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;answer-text__paragraph&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5rem; font-family: &amp;quot;I